            <lg xml:id="TK652">
<l>eṉṟu moruvutal vēṇṭum pukaḻoṭu </l>
<l> naṉṟi payavā viṉai</l>            
            </lg>
            <lg xml:lang="en">
<l>Ministers should at all times avoid acts which, in addition to fame, yield no benefit (for the future).</l>
